==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Engrosser
<hw>En*gross"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One
who copies a writing in large, fair characters.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who takes the whole; a person who purchases such
quantities of articles in a market as to raise the price; a
forestaller.</def> <rj><au>Locke.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>engrossing</ent>⟦br⟧
